{"tid":2482035,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月百合番】BLUE REFLECTION RAY/澪","createTime":"2021-04-09T16:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T07:42:16.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3f79fddf814ddd524b40f79f2109eed0e79c6f5e","tid":2482035,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW5raRRFgh4FSKUB6AQfiQ9xtt2hVS1NjcvSZtY16yAUT?filename=A0h3c3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0h3c3z.jpg&h=015bb6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaqdG62FCXkQCJHaBQMfeqBGMxwJs5dby6dRojWvsewoS?filename=xZdRmZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZdRmZD.jpg&h=da69f351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《BLUE REFLECTION RAY/澪》是由J.C.STAFF製作的一部原創動畫。<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：<br />\n喜悅、悲傷、憤怒&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n思想，是每個人都擁有的，但是眼睛看不見的力量。<br />\n這種力量有時甚至能改變世界。<br />\n<br />\n總是積極向前，遇到有困難的人一定不會置之不理的平原陽櫻璃，想和別人搞好關係卻不知道怎麼相處的，笨手笨腳的羽成瑠夏。<br />\n可以說是對比鮮明的兩個少女的相遇，將會如何改變她們自身及世界呢&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n以2017年發售的《BLUE REFLECTION 幻舞少女之劍》作為原點，<br />\n作為新「BLUE REFLECTION」企劃展開的電視動畫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4WOuJGmG-wI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WOuJGmG-wI&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=c9afcee7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WOuJGmG-wI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/97TRoHo8Mzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F97TRoHo8Mzk&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=5f09691d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/97TRoHo8Mzk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LGDDcFjCLFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLGDDcFjCLFU&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=df265699\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LGDDcFjCLFU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Chx1FfBJoCk\